[[Image:RC-12 Manual.JPG|right|300px|thumb|Yokobori (Yokomo) RC-12 manual]]
'''Mini Racer RC-12''' is 1/12 scale [[RC car]] manufactured by [[Yokomo]] from 1977 to the early 1980s. It was produced when [[Yokomo#History|Yokobori Mokei]] changed their name to Yokomo. The RC-12 box had both a Yokomo and Yokobori Mokei label on it. There were two different models in the RC-12 series. "Mini Racer RC-12" came with a narrow [[chassis]] and "Mini Racer RC-12 Junior" came with a wide chassis.
