[[File:Munakata Shiko Memorial Museum of Art.jpg|thumb|Munakata Shiko Memorial Museum of Art]]
The {{nihongo|'''Munakata Shiko Memorial Museum of Art'''|棟方志功記念館|Munakata Shikō Kinenkan}} is a museum located in [[Aomori, Aomori|Aomori]], [[Aomori Prefecture]], [[Japan]].  It features works from [[Shikō Munakata]], a [[Woodblock printing in Japan|woodblock printmaker]] who was born in Aomori City.  The museum was opened in 1975.

